  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This interventional study seeks to evaluate the overall outcomes of a novel, integrated yoga
      based intervention for people with chronic musculoskeletal pain and assess the experience of
      patient to the self care using yoga practices.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
